OnCalendar=Sun,Mon,Tue,Wed,Thu 07:12:00 UTC
OnCalendar=Sun,Mon,Tue,Wed,Thu 07:18:00 UTC
OnCalendar=Sun,Mon,Tue,Wed,Thu 07:24:00 UTC
