OnCalendar=Sun,Mon,Tue,Wed,Thu 07:54:00 UTC
OnCalendar=Sun,Mon,Tue,Wed,Thu 08:00:00 UTC
OnCalendar=Sun,Mon,Tue,Wed,Thu 08:06:00 UTC
